    "image_with_text_p4fRFK": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_84tiUa": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q:</strong> What does a perfect, unhurried morning look like for each of you right now?</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>Colin: </strong>As a single dad, I would love an unhurried morning where I don't need to get everything ready to take my son to school. However, I grew to enjoy waking up early to give myself time and not having to rush through tasks. After dropping him off, I would come to our shop and make myself a flat white to complete the perfect morning routine.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>Paul: </strong>A not-too-early Saturday wake up, making pour-overs for my partner and me with some classical music playing in the background. Then it’s brunch with friends, followed by a long walk through Stanley Park with my dog Norman. Hard to beat that, really.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
